# Water Treatment CPS Cyber-Physical Simulator & Attack Testbed

A Cyber-Physical System (CPS) simulation of an Industrial Control System (ICS) based **water treatment plant**, designed to generate realistic operational datasets and simulate cyber-attacks on PLC-controlled infrastructure.

This project integrates:

- PLC process simulation using **CODESYS Structured Text**
- **Modbus TCP communication**
- **Automated dataset generation**
- **Cyber-attack simulation**
- **Machine learning based intrusion detection**
- **Real-time anomaly detection**

The platform allows researchers and students to generate labeled ICS datasets and evaluate machine learning approaches for detecting attacks in cyber-physical water systems.

---

