# System Architecture

```
                +-----------------------+
                |     PLC Controller    |
                |   (CODESYS ST Code)   |
                +-----------+-----------+
                            |
                        Modbus TCP
                            |
                +-----------v-----------+
                |    Python Data Logger |
                | Dataset Generator     |
                +-----------+-----------+
                            |
                +-----------v-----------+
                |   Attack Simulation   |
                |   Python Scripts      |
                +-----------+-----------+
                            |
                     Generated Dataset
                            |
                +-----------v-----------+
                | Feature Engineering   |
                +-----------+-----------+
                            |
                +-----------v-----------+
                | ML Training Pipeline  |
                +-----------+-----------+
                            |
                +-----------v-----------+
                | Real-Time Intrusion   |
                | Detection System      |
                +-----------------------+
```

---

# Water Treatment Process Simulation

The system simulates a simplified industrial water treatment plant.

## Stage 1 — Raw Water Intake
- Raw water tank
- Pump operation
- Level monitoring

## Stage 2 — Chemical Treatment
- pH monitoring
- Chemical dosing control

## Stage 3 — Filtration
- Flow rate control
- Filtration process

## Stage 4 — Storage & Distribution
- Final water storage tank
- Overflow detection
- Output flow control

### Sensors monitored

```
Tank Level
Flow Rate
pH Value
Pump Status
Valve State
Chemical Dosing
Overflow Events
```

